#. <section class="sutta" id="sn56.7"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.7:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.7:0.2"
msgid "1. Samādhivagga"
msgstr "1. Immersion"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn56.7:0.3"
msgid "7. Vitakkasutta"
msgstr "7. Thoughts"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.418"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: vitakkeyyātha → vitakketha (bj, s1-3, km)
msgctxt "sn56.7:1.1"
msgid "“Mā, bhikkhave, pāpake akusale vitakke vitakkeyyātha, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr "“Mendicants, don’t think bad, unskillful thoughts, such as"

msgctxt "sn56.7:1.2"
msgid "kāmavitakkaṃ, byāpādavitakkaṃ, vihiṃsāvitakkaṃ."
msgstr "sensual, malicious, and cruel thoughts."

msgctxt "sn56.7:1.3"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "sn56.7:1.4"
msgid ""
"Nete, bhikkhave, vitakkā atthasaṃhitā nādibrahmacariyakā na nibbidāya na "
"virāgāya na nirodhāya na upasamāya na abhiññāya na sambodhāya na nibbānāya "
"saṃvattanti."
msgstr ""
"Because those thoughts aren’t beneficial or relevant to the fundamentals of "
"the spiritual life. They don’t lead to disillusionment, dispassion, "
"cessation, peace, insight, awakening, and extinguishment."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.7:2.1"
msgid ""
"Vitakkentā ca kho tumhe, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti vitakkeyyātha, ‘ayaṃ "
"dukkhasamudayo’ti vitakkeyyātha, ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodho’ti vitakkeyyātha, ‘ayaṃ "
"dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti vitakkeyyātha."
msgstr ""
"When you think, you should think: ‘This is suffering’ … ‘This is the origin "
"of suffering’ … ‘This is the cessation of suffering’ … ‘This is the practice "
"that leads to the cessation of suffering’."

msgctxt "sn56.7:2.2"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "sn56.7:2.3"
msgid ""
"Ete, bhikkhave, vitakkā atthasaṃhitā ete ādibrahmacariyakā ete nibbidāya "
"virāgāya nirodhāya upasamāya abhiññāya sambodhāya nibbānāya saṃvattanti."
msgstr ""
"Because those thoughts are beneficial and relevant to the fundamentals of "
"the spiritual life. They lead to disillusionment, dispassion, cessation, "
"peace, insight, awakening, and extinguishment."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.7:3.1"
msgid ""
"Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe … ‘ayaṃ "
"dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti."
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.7:3.2"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
